name: Polymarket
fullText: BREAKING: U.S. HOUSE PASSES BILL TO END LONGEST SHUTDOWN IN HISTORY.

name: Polymarket
fullText: BREAKING: Trump will sign bill ending the shutdown tonight at 9:45pm ET.

name: Polymarket
fullText:
BREAKING: The last U.S. penny to ever be created was minted today. 

It has officially been discontinued.
